{"tid":2086933,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中共而家驚過你，柒婆今晚訓唔著","createTime":"2020-06-30T13:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T15:09:28.000Z","uid":240372,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"70a89a084ac3b9f6eebe9736995e163e8a2559cd","tid":2086933,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"係無限限聚令情況底下，可以想像聽日d狗會幾咁大力打壓，會幾咁無理咁濫捕<br />\n配合埋國安法係冇條文既情況底下都要急急腳咁係7.1前出，<br />\n呢一切，都係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共唔想香港人再造一次2百萬人奇蹟，俾國際社會理由去參與香港事項。</span></span></span><br />\n所以！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日無論係因為<br />\n1）要對得住死去，被捕手足<br />\n2）俾藉口國際社會<br />\n3）為自己最後一次發聲<br />\n<br />\n請大家一家大細出晒黎！人越多越安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2點維園見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cdb582d4a897f0b0aa929cd40a5867678f97fa84","tid":2086933,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0vodRn.png&amp;h=bffec503&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z74Hva5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ74Hva5.png&h=a1d38e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"faad4d743bb4710a88cd3ebf9c7b837c472fa098","tid":2086933,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"推，香港人報仇！"},{"pid":"e67defdc18c02e87ce176f03c2e5691cf95260a8","tid":2086933,"uid":138594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"7.1 聽日見"},{"pid":"b12764bdeefaae23fa281d9845ca7f531c41d95f","tid":2086933,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e67defdc18c02e87ce176f03c2e5691cf95260a8","tid":2086933,"uid":138594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"7.1 聽日見"},"citedBy":0,"r